data.enText: a stick used for playing a drum

data.chText: 熟鸡（或家禽）腿下段；下段鸡（或家禽）腿肉
data.enText: the lower part of the leg of a chicken or other bird that is cooked and eaten as food

tr: a stick used for playing a drum
the lower joint of the leg of a fowl

value.def: A drumstick is the lower part of the leg of a bird such as a chicken which is cooked and eaten.
Drumsticks are sticks used for beating a drum.
